      • assertTrue

        public static void assertTrue(boolean b)
        Assert that the given boolean value is true.
        参数:
        b - the value to test
        抛出:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if b is false

      • assertFalse

        public static void assertFalse(boolean b)
        Assert that the given boolean value is false.
        参数:
        b - the value to test
        抛出:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if b is true

      • assertEquals

        public static void assertEquals(java.lang.Object expected,
                                java.lang.Object actual)
        Assert that a given object is equal to the expected value for the object.
        参数:
        expected - the expected value of an object for equality testing
        actual - the actual value of the object to compare with the expected value
        抛出:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if expected is not equal to actual, i.e. throws AssertionError if expected.equals(actual) is false

      • assertNotEqual

        public static void assertNotEqual(java.lang.Object obj1,
                                  java.lang.Object obj2)
        Assert that the two objects are not equal.
        参数:
        obj1 - an object to test for not being equal to another
        obj2 - an object to test for not being equal to another
        抛出:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if obj1 is equal to obj2, i.e. throws AssertionError if obj1.equals(obj2) is true

      • assertNull

        public static void assertNull(java.lang.Object o)
        Assert that an object is null.
        参数:
        o - the object to test for nullity
        抛出:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if o is not null

      • assertNotNull

        public static void assertNotNull(java.lang.Object o)
        Assert that an object is not null.
        参数:
        o - the object to test for non-nullity
        抛出:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if o is null

      • assertExpectedThrowable

        public static void assertExpectedThrowable(java.lang.Class<? extends java.lang.Throwable> expectedClass,
                                           java.lang.Throwable t)
        Assert that a given Throwable is of the same type as the given expected Throwable class.
        参数:
        expectedClass - the expected class of the Throwable
        t - the Throwable to compare type against expectedClass
        抛出:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if t is not an instance of expectedClass

      • assertNotReached

        public static void assertNotReached()
        Asserts that a line of code should not be reached.
        抛出:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if reach line in code that should not be executed
